<p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.3em;text-align:left;">Helpmate</p>

<h1 style="color:#222;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:normal;line-height:normal;">Reset your Helpmate password</h1>

<p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.3em;text-align:left;">
Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,
</p>

<p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.3em;text-align:left;">
Can't remember your password? Don't worry about it.
</p>

<p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.3em;text-align:left;">
Your username is:<br />
<b><%= @user.username %></b>
</p>

<p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.3em;text-align:left;">
<b>Just click this link to reset your password:</b><br />
<%= edit_password_reset_url(@user.password_reset_token) %>
</p>

<hr />

<p style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.3em;text-align:left;">
<strong>Didn't ask to reset your password?</strong><br />
If you didn't ask for your password, it's likely that another user entered your email address by mistake while trying to reset their
password. If that's the case, you don't need to take any further action and can safely disregard this email.
</p>
